video.title: On My Block
video.synopsis: In a rough Los Angeles neighborhood, four smart, funny and streetwise teens find their lifelong friendship tested as they begin high school.

episodes.synopsis: As the first day of high school approaches, Monse returns from writing camp to find that Ruby and Jamal are on the outs with Cesar.
episodes.title: Chapter One

episodes.synopsis: An attempted intervention on Cesar's behalf doesn't go quite as planned. Meanwhile, Ruby experiences love at first sight with a friend of the family.
episodes.title: Chapter Two

episodes.synopsis: As Cesar sinks deeper into Oscar's unsafe world, the group deals with the emotional turmoil of attending their first high school dance.
episodes.title: Chapter Three

episodes.synopsis: On Halloween, Jamal persuades the crew to trick-or-treat in swanky Brentwood, where he hopes to uncover clues to a local mystery.
episodes.title: Chapter Four

episodes.synopsis: Self-confessed blabbermouth Jamal gives Cesar a time limit to tell Ruby about what happened with Olivia, but a police lockdown complicates matters.
episodes.title: Chapter Five

episodes.synopsis: As secrets get revealed, the core friend group begins to fracture. Amid the upheaval, Jamal's lies about football finally catch up with him.
episodes.title: Chapter Six

episodes.synopsis: Ruby becomes obsessed with planning the perfect quinceañera for Olivia, while Jamal finds an oddball ally in his quest to solve the RollerWorld riddle.
episodes.title: Chapter Seven

episodes.synopsis: Cesar spends quality time with Oscar, Monse finagles a baby-sitting job, Jamal edges closer to the truth, and Olivia experiences a fashion crisis.
episodes.title: Chapter Eight

episodes.synopsis: With Cesar's future on the line, Jamal, Monse and Ruby end up in a frantic search around town to find the one thing that might save him.
episodes.title: Chapter Nine

episodes.synopsis: Partners switch on more than the dance floor at Olivia's quinceañera, but an act of mercy could cost the friends everything they hold dear.
episodes.title: Chapter Ten

episodes.synopsis: On New Year's Eve, Monse makes a promise that leaves Cesar at loose ends, Jamal keeps an eye on the money, and Ruby's brother returns with a surprise.
episodes.title: Chapter Eleven

episodes.synopsis: While Jamal, Monse and Cesar search for the missing stash, Ruby's grief progresses into anger, leading him to lash out at a dangerous acquaintance.
episodes.title: Chapter Twelve

episodes.synopsis: An increasingly anxious Jamal pays a price for unearthing the money. Monse finds a way to help Cesar, and Ruby sends Jasmine on an impossible errand.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirteen

episodes.synopsis: Cesar and Jamal make strange bedfellows, Jasmine helps Ruby find a date for the Valentine's Day dance, and Monse receives a heartbreaking ultimatum.
episodes.title: Chapter Fourteen

episodes.synopsis: An attempt to raise Ruby's spirits works a little too well. Cesar gets advice about Monse. Jamal urges Ruby's grandmother to seek medical care.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifteen

episodes.synopsis: Unsure about accepting Julia's offer, Monse invites Ruby and Jamal over to help her figure things out, but their visit doesn't quite go as planned.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixteen

episodes.synopsis: Baby shower preparations bring out the worst in Ruby's mom. Guilty consciences plague Mario and Cesar, and Jamal worries that the money may be cursed.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventeen

episodes.synopsis: As an old enemy returns to the neighborhood, the friends zero in on a solution to both their dirty money problem and Cesar's unstable living situation.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighteen

episodes.synopsis: With Cesar's options dwindling, he takes drastic measures, prompting his worried friends to put their own Hail Mary plan into motion.
episodes.title: Chapter Nineteen

episodes.synopsis: Cesar meets his fate head-on, but friendship lines are drawn when he tries to put things right with Monse, who comes to a decision about her future.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty

episodes.synopsis: After being snatched off the street, Monse, Jamal, Ruby and Cesar come face to face with their kidnapper, who makes them an offer they can't refuse.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-One

episodes.synopsis: The group's new mission brings out Jamal's control issues. Oscar seethes when Cesar bonds with their unexpected houseguest. Jasmine makes over Monse.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Two

episodes.synopsis: Jamal gets up close and personal with his suspected stalker. Ruby's moneymaking scheme violates health codes. Monse overindulges with Jasmine.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Three

episodes.synopsis: As the crew narrows down the list of suspects, Cesar asks Monse out on a real date, Ruby stresses over a growing attraction, and Jamal seeks sex advice.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Four

episodes.synopsis: While supporting Monse through a crisis, Jamal zeroes in on a new lead, and Ruby loses his cool. Meanwhile, Oscar tries to negotiate with Cuchillos.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Five

episodes.synopsis: When an old mixtape provides a major clue, the crew infiltrates a music video shoot, where confessions are made, lips are locked, and secrets revealed.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Six

episodes.synopsis: After realizing Cuchillos's endgame, the group puts a desperate — and dangerous — plan into motion that tests the limits of their loyalty and friendship.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: A fraught hike into the woods and a startling discovery pushes the crew toward some difficult decisions that will change their friendship — and future.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: When Jamal muscles in on Ruby's dream of being senior class president, Jasmine goes on the offensive. Oscar warns Cesar of the dangers that lie ahead.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Jamal reconnects with an old friend after the class election turns ugly. Ruby feels smothered by Jasmine's attentions, and Cesar sends Oscar a message.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty

episodes.synopsis: Back in Freeridge for the holidays, Monse receives a rude reminder about why she left. Ruby and Jasmine turn to their friends for relationship advice.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-One

episodes.synopsis: A long-buried secret lands the four friends in hot water. After confronting Monse over a butt dial, Jamal makes an unexpected connection.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Two

episodes.synopsis: Ruby obsesses over Jasmine's mystery man, Cesar deals with dissension in the ranks, and the arrival of sinister-looking letters worries everyone.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Three

episodes.synopsis: With emotions running high, Ruby, Jamal and Monse come clean as Cesar contemplates revenge. Jasmine, meanwhile, prioritizes self-care.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Four

episodes.synopsis: Monse, Jamal and Ruby help Cesar with a grim task during an emotional day that sees relationships change, secrets divulged and decisions made.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Five

episodes.synopsis: After a wild night, Jamal wakes with a fuzzy memory, Monse jumps to the wrong conclusion about Cesar, and Ruby decides to get something off his chest.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Six

episodes.synopsis: With the prom fast approaching, Jamal searches for the perfect theme and Ruby stresses over finding the perfect date. Abuelita fesses up.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: As Jamal tries to figure out who's following him and Ruby's prom preparations go awry, the friends come together for a final celebration.
episodes.title: The Final Chapter
